{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/tip-of-redirecting-the-command-svn-diff","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c757ec47-4ea7-5fb6-84e9-2735b5bbde9d","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/4b190/svn-diff.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/8ac56/svn-diff.webp 240w,\n/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/d3be9/svn-diff.webp 480w,\n/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/d00b9/svn-diff.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/09b79/svn-diff.jpg 240w,\n/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/7cc5e/svn-diff.jpg 480w,\n/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/4b190/svn-diff.jpg 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/4b190/svn-diff.jpg\"\n            alt=\"svn-diff\"\n            title=\"svn-diff\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\nThe default output mode of <strong>svn diff</strong> is verbose. If you have many modifications, it is sometimes difficult to see the differences.\nFuntunately, <em>svn</em> has provided options for customizing <strong>svn diff</strong> output.</p>\n<p>To change the output of <strong>svn diff</strong>, we need a script file (such as <strong>svndiff.sh</strong>) with following content,</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/sh</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">DIFF</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/usr/bin/vimdiff\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Subversion provides the paths we need as the sixth and seventh parameters</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">LEFT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">${6}</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">RIGHT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">${7}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># diff command</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">${DIFF}</span> <span class=\"token variable\">${LEFT}</span> <span class=\"token variable\">${RIGHT}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then modify the svn configuration file <strong>~/.subversion/config</strong> and make sure the following configuration is written:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[helpers]\ndiff-cmd = /path/to/svndiff.sh</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then, <strong>svn diff</strong> will call the <strong>svndiff.sh</strong> script, which uses <em>vimdiff</em> in <em>svn</em> difference mode.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2013-06-25---Tip-of-Redirecting-the-Command-\"svn diff\"//posts/tip-of-redirecting-the-command-svn-diff","tagSlugs":["/tag/programming/","/tag/svn/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2013-06-25T11:25:00.000+0800","description":"tips of redirecting svn diff to help coding.","tags":["Programming","SVN"],"title":"Tip of Redirecting the Command \"svn diff\"","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/f0db4ae35e5b28b9aa3720b89294dea6/svn-diff.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2013-06-25---Tip-of-Redirecting-the-Command-\"svn diff\"//posts/tip-of-redirecting-the-command-svn-diff"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2764776372","401334301"]}